snippet.title: Comparison: Clockwork Knight (NA / Pepperouchau no Fukubukuro version)
snippet.description: A short video I did out of curiosity/for fun comparing the North American version of Clockwork Knight 1 (left side) with the version found in the bundle release Clockwork Knight: Pepperouchau no Fukubukuro (right side), which runs on Clockwork Knight 2's engine. Audio is from the North American version.
